      "role": "user",
      "content": "the roots actually look kinda stunted and weirdly tangled... like things have been moving around in there. is it normal for the soil to feel like it's been disturbed or for there to be lots of little holes or tunnels near the roots? i'm worried something is eating them or messing with the roots underground.",
